text:
"It's probably past the time when lessons end. If you're
heading home, I'd appreciate it if you let me know."

......
So you're still here after all...

I wondered what happened when I didn't hear from
you at the time...

Well then, I'll head back.
Let me know when you're done.

That lax attitude...
You might regret it someday.

Maybe... but Luca wanted to do it until satisfied, right?
Well, let's not overdo it...
